OL,3,CWhere UK weather warnings are in place
OL,4,Cahead of thunderstorms
OL,6,FTwo yellow thunderstorm warnings were
OL,7,Fin place on Sunday evening and further
OL,8,Fwarnings for heavy rainfall have been
OL,9,Fissued for parts of the country on
OL,10,FMonday.
OL,12,Fafter Manchester United's 1-0 defeat
OL,13,Fto Arsenal on Sunday caused water to
OL,14,Fpour from the corner of the roof. The
OL,15,Fclub said 41mm of rain fell in the two
OL,16,Fhours after the final whistle. By
OL,17,Fcontrast, throughout May last year,
OL,18,F29mm fell on Old Trafford.
