OL,3,CWhere UK weather warnings are in place
OL,4,Cahead of thunderstorms
OL,6,FHonor Criswick, a meteorologist at the
OL,7,FMet Office, said forecast storms might
OL,8,F"band together" in areas across the
OL,9,FUK, resulting in intense bursts of
OL,10,Flightning and heavy rainfall.
OL,12,FShe said: "In the areas with heavy
OL,13,Fshowers, it's expected to get a bit
OL,14,Fgustier as well, and surface water
OL,15,Fflooding is also a possibility."
OL,17,FSpells of heavy rain are also expected
OL,18,Fto hit eastern areas of Northern
OL,19,FIreland on Monday, with a warning in
OL,20,Fplace from 12pm until 6am on Tuesday.
