OL,3,CWhere UK weather warnings are in place
OL,4,Cahead of thunderstorms
OL,6,FIn areas of south west England,
OL,7,Fincluding Cornwall and Exeter, heavy
OL,8,Frain is likely to bring some transport
OL,9,Fdisruption and possible flooding in a
OL,10,Ffew places between 8am and midnight on
OL,11,FMonday.
OL,13,FThe same warning is in place for
OL,14,Fsouthern Wales on Monday, where heavy
OL,15,Frain is forecast for areas including
OL,16,FSwansea and Cardiff between 8am and
OL,17,Fmidnight.
OL,19,FMs Criswick said these storms are
OL,20,Flikely to mean there is a week of
OL,21,Fmilder weather ahead.
