OL,3,CWhere UK weather warnings are in place
OL,4,Cahead of thunderstorms
OL,6,FShe said: "It will still be fairly
OL,7,Fwarm, with temperatures in the high
OL,8,Fteens and early 20s, but cooler than
OL,9,Fit has been over the past few days."
OL,11,FThe temperature records for the year
OL,12,Fwere broken three times over the past
OL,13,Fweek, with Thursday, Saturday and then
OL,14,FSunday seeing increasingly hot
OL,15,Ftemperatures across the country.
